Members.Title: Metro - Owner
Members.Description: He is the owner of Modworlds. Metro manages the discord server, organizes projects and creates unique modpacks. He also loves to troll people sometimes.

Members.Title: Ogeran - Owner
Members.Description: He is also the owner of Modworlds. Ogeran mostly manages the coding stuff, logistics and designs digital tools for Modworlds.

Members.Title: Wchtig_ - Manager and Bot Dev.
Members.Description: Wchtig is our most active moderator. He does setup commandblocks on maps we build for our projects and manages the activity of the team. Moreover he supports Modworlds through his social media.

Members.Title: Ari - Head moderator
Members.Description: Ari is one of our head moderators. He designs and plans projects.

Members.Title: Stabschrecke - Moderator
Members.Description: A moderator from Modworlds. He keeps our discord safe and enjoys playing our projects.

Members.Title: TechnoCatza - Project leader
Members.Description: He owns the project 'SMP Saga'. It's a discord server with many different one-at-a-time projects!

Members.Title: Ma_Do - Project leader
Members.Description: Ma_Do is a brand new project leader. He owns the project called 'War of Ritopia'.
